# Database Rules

- Schema: `packages/database/prisma/schema.prisma`
- UUID PKs, `snake_case` columns (`@map`), soft deletes (`deletedAt`) where applicable
- Migrations in `prisma/migrations/` — never edit applied migrations
- Repositories in `packages/database/src/repositories/`; export via `createRepositories()`
- Cursor pagination via `paginateWithCursor` from `packages/database/src/pagination`
- Seed permissions in `packages/database/src/seed.ts` when adding RBAC keys
- Zod schemas in `@varnarc/validation` mirror API inputs

Copy-paste prompt: `cursor/prompts/database.md`
